text: Novoyadgarovskaya () is a rural locality (a village) in Krivle-Ilyushkinsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Yermolayevo, 7 km from Krivle-Ilyushkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novoyadgarovskaya
